panelsJSON.title: Top 10 Source IP with Highest Alerts [Logs Splunk]
Top 10 Destination IP with Highest Alerts [Logs Splunk]

params.markdown:
**Overview**

These visualizations provide a comprehensive analysis of Splunk alert data. They include bar charts to show alerts by host, source, event reason, user, and alert name, offering insights into where and why alerts are occurring. Pie charts represent the severity of alerts, actions taken, and OS distribution. Line charts visualize alerts over time, helping to identify trends or spikes. Tables display detailed information on the top 10 destination and source IPs with the highest alerts. This set of visualizations enables effective monitoring, prioritization, and investigation of potential issues and threats.
